## JSONStore.key property

Same as `Storage.key`

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
key: (index: number) => string;
```

## Example


```ts
local.set('foo', 123)
local.set('bar', 234)
local.key(0) // => 'foo'
local.key(1) // => 'bar'

```
